
	Kevin Hedderwick has resigned as COO and executive director of JSE-listed Long4Life to pursue personal interests. 
	Hedderwick, who was previously CEO of Famous Brands, joined Long4Life in May. 
	“I would like to personally thank Kevin for his short, but significant contribution and guidance to the initial phase of Long4Life’s formation and early acquisitions. We wish him well for the future,” chairperson Brian Joffe said in a statement. 